Localization.Title: This Way or That?
Localization.Text:
Kindness and forgiveness, masters!” the creature gurgles and prostrates before you. “Masters are looking for...Baggins?”

Finally.

“Orcses go to hill of haunted stones, with slaveses. Orcses take Baggins too, precious. But Smeagol knows trails in woodses. Find orcses and Baggins. Follow Smeagol to find Baggins?”  Sensing your hesitation, he pleads pitifully “Trust Smeagol?”
